    <entry>
      <title>Markdown高级特性</title>
      <link href="/2022/04/28/Markdown%E9%AB%98%E7%BA%A7%E7%89%B9%E6%80%A7/"/>
      <url>/2022/04/28/Markdown%E9%AB%98%E7%BA%A7%E7%89%B9%E6%80%A7/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="高级语法"><a href="#高级语法" class="headerlink" title="高级语法"></a>高级语法</h1><h2 id="数学公式"><a href="#数学公式" class="headerlink" title="数学公式"></a>数学公式</h2><ol><li>行内公式 $公式$</li><li>行间公式 $$公式$$</li></ol><p>符号速查可参考<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/mengsuenyan/p/12614058.html">Markdown数学符号速查表</a></p><h2 id="流程图"><a href="#流程图" class="headerlink" title="流程图"></a>流程图</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">st=&gt;start: 开始</span><br><span class="line">op1=&gt;operation: 操作</span><br><span class="line">c=&gt;condition: 是 or 否</span><br><span class="line">e=&gt;end: 结束</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">st-&gt;op1-&gt;c</span><br><span class="line">c(yes)-&gt;e</span><br><span class="line">c(no)-&gt;op1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下  </p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">st=&gt;start: 开始</span><br><span class="line">op1=&gt;operation: 操作</span><br><span class="line">c=&gt;condition: 是 or 否</span><br><span class="line">e=&gt;end: 结束</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">st-&gt;op1-&gt;c</span><br><span class="line">c(yes)-&gt;e</span><br><span class="line">c(no)-&gt;op1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="ToDo-List"><a href="#ToDo-List" class="headerlink" title="ToDo List"></a>ToDo List</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> [] 未处理1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> [] 未处理2</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> [x] 已处理1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> [x] 已处理1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>[] 未处理1</li><li>[] 未处理2</li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> 已处理1</li><li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> 已处理1</li></ul><h2 id="序列图"><a href="#序列图" class="headerlink" title="序列图"></a>序列图</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">A-&gt;B: hello?</span><br><span class="line">Note right of B: B thinks</span><br><span class="line">B-&gt;A: hello!</span><br><span class="line">```  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">## 甘特图</span><br><span class="line">```gantt         </span><br><span class="line">       dateFormat  YYYY-MM-DD   </span><br><span class="line">       title 使用mermaid语言定制甘特图</span><br><span class="line">       section 任务1</span><br><span class="line">       已完成的任务           :done,    des1, 2014-01-06,2014-01-08</span><br><span class="line">       正在进行的任务               :active,  des2, 2014-01-09, 3d</span><br><span class="line">       待完成任务1               :         des3, after des2, 5d</span><br><span class="line">       待完成任务2              :         des4, after des3, 5d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> Tutorial </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> Markdown </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>Markdown进阶语法（hexo部分不支持）</title>
      <link href="/2022/04/28/Markdown%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/"/>
      <url>/2022/04/28/Markdown%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="1-进阶语法"><a href="#1-进阶语法" class="headerlink" title="1. 进阶语法"></a>1. 进阶语法</h1><h2 id="1-1-换行"><a href="#1-1-换行" class="headerlink" title="1.1. 换行"></a>1.1. 换行</h2><p>连续两个以上空格+回车</p><h2 id="1-2-缩进字符"><a href="#1-2-缩进字符" class="headerlink" title="1.2. 缩进字符"></a>1.2. 缩进字符</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&amp;#160;1/4个中文缩进</span><br><span class="line">&amp;#8194;半个中文缩进，1字符</span><br><span class="line">&amp;#8195;1个中文缩进，2字符</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>未缩进<br>&amp;#160;1&#x2F;4个中文缩进<br>&amp;#8194;半个中文缩进，1字符<br>&amp;#8195;1个中文缩进，2字符</p><h2 id="1-3-特殊符号"><a href="#1-3-特殊符号" class="headerlink" title="1.3. 特殊符号"></a>1.3. 特殊符号</h2><h3 id="1-3-1"><a href="#1-3-1" class="headerlink" title="1.3.1. \"></a>1.3.1. \</h3><p>显示字符本身</p><h3 id="1-3-2-其他符号"><a href="#1-3-2-其他符号" class="headerlink" title="1.3.2. 其他符号"></a>1.3.2. 其他符号</h3><p>具体可参考<a href="https://www.axihe.com/tools/markdown/with-html/special-symbol.html">markdown特殊符号</a><br>与<a href="https://unicode-table.com/cn/">Unicode字符码查询</a></p><table><thead><tr><th>命令</th><th>效果</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>&amp;#10084;</code></td><td>&amp;#10084;</td></tr><tr><td><code>&amp;#10003;</code></td><td>&amp;#10003;</td></tr><tr><td><code>&amp;#10004;</code></td><td>&amp;#10004;</td></tr><tr><td><code>&amp;#10005;</code></td><td>&amp;#10005;</td></tr><tr><td><code>&amp;#1;</code></td><td>&amp;#1;</td></tr><tr><td><code>&amp;#9742;</code></td><td>&amp;#9742;</td></tr><tr><td><code>&amp;#5748;</code></td><td>&amp;#5748;</td></tr><tr><td><code>&amp;#5223;</code></td><td>&amp;#5223;</td></tr><tr><td><code>&amp;#8734;</code></td><td>&amp;#8734;</td></tr><tr><td><code>&amp;#10008;</code></td><td>&amp;#10008;</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="1-4-字体、字号与颜色"><a href="#1-4-字体、字号与颜色" class="headerlink" title="1.4. 字体、字号与颜色"></a>1.4. 字体、字号与颜色</h2><p>通过内嵌HTML代码实现字体特效,字体大小(size)范围<font color=#0099ff face="黑体" size=5>[1,7]</font><br>对字体颜色的修改可查询<a href="http://xh.5156edu.com/page/z1015m9220j18754.html">HTML颜色代码表</a></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">color</span>=<span class="string">#0099ff</span> <span class="attr">face</span>=<span class="string">&quot;黑体&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span>color=#0099ff 黑体字体<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">face</span>=<span class="string">&quot;微软雅黑&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span>微软雅黑字体<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">face</span>=<span class="string">&quot;STCAIYUN&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span>华为彩云<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">color</span>=<span class="string">#0099ff</span> <span class="attr">size</span>=<span class="string">1</span> <span class="attr">face</span>=<span class="string">&quot;黑体&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span>size=1<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">color</span>=<span class="string">#0099ff</span> <span class="attr">size</span>=<span class="string">2</span> <span class="attr">face</span>=<span class="string">&quot;黑体&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span>size=2<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">color</span>=<span class="string">#0099ff</span> <span class="attr">size</span>=<span class="string">3</span> <span class="attr">face</span>=<span class="string">&quot;黑体&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span>size=3<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">color</span>=<span class="string">#0099ff</span> <span class="attr">size</span>=<span class="string">4</span> <span class="attr">face</span>=<span class="string">&quot;黑体&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span>size=4<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">color</span>=<span class="string">#0099ff</span> <span class="attr">size</span>=<span class="string">5</span> <span class="attr">face</span>=<span class="string">&quot;黑体&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span>size=5<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">color</span>=<span class="string">#0099ff</span> <span class="attr">size</span>=<span class="string">6</span> <span class="attr">face</span>=<span class="string">&quot;黑体&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span>size=6<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">color</span>=<span class="string">#0099ff</span> <span class="attr">size</span>=<span class="string">7</span> <span class="attr">face</span>=<span class="string">&quot;黑体&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span>size=7<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span>  </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><font color=#0099ff face="黑体">color&#x3D;#0099ff 黑体字体</font><br><font face="微软雅黑">微软雅黑字体</font><br><font face="STCAIYUN">华为彩云</font><br><font color=#0099ff size=1 face="黑体">size&#x3D;1</font><br><font color=#0099ff size=2 face="黑体">size&#x3D;2</font><br><font color=#0099ff size=3 face="黑体">size&#x3D;3</font><br><font color=#0099ff size=4 face="黑体">size&#x3D;4</font><br><font color=#0099ff size=5 face="黑体">size&#x3D;5</font><br><font color=#0099ff size=6 face="黑体">size&#x3D;6</font><br><font color=#0099ff size=7 face="黑体">size&#x3D;7</font>  </p><h2 id="1-5-注脚"><a href="#1-5-注脚" class="headerlink" title="1.5. 注脚"></a>1.5. 注脚</h2><p>在需要添加注脚的文字后加上脚注名字[^注脚名字],称为加注。 然后在文本的任意位置(一般在最后)添加脚注，脚注前必须有对应的脚注名字。<br>示范如下：</p><blockquote><p>注意需要添加空格！</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">脚注演示段落[^1]，需要演示一下脚注的使用方法[^2]  </span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">[<span class="symbol">^1</span>]: <span class="link">脚注1  </span></span><br><span class="line">[<span class="symbol">^2</span>]: <span class="link">脚注2</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>脚注演示段落<a href="%E8%84%9A%E6%B3%A81">^1</a>，需要演示一下脚注的使用方法<a href="%E8%84%9A%E6%B3%A82">^2</a>  </p><h2 id="1-6-背景色"><a href="#1-6-背景色" class="headerlink" title="1.6. 背景色"></a>1.6. 背景色</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">table</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span> <span class="attr">bgcolor</span>=<span class="string">orange</span>&gt;</span></span>背景色是：orange<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">table</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><tr><td bgcolor=orange>背景色是：orange</td></tr></table><h2 id="1-7-emoji表情"><a href="#1-7-emoji表情" class="headerlink" title="1.7. emoji表情"></a>1.7. emoji表情</h2><p>emoji表情使用:EMOJICODE:的格式，详细列表可见<a href="https://www.webpagefx.com/tools/emoji-cheat-sheet/">Emoji cheat sheet</a></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">:smile:  </span><br><span class="line">:blush:  </span><br><span class="line">:heart<span class="emphasis">_eyes:  </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">:flushed:  </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">:stuck_</span>out<span class="emphasis">_tongue_</span>closed<span class="emphasis">_eyes:</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>:smile:<br>:blush:<br>:heart_eyes:<br>:flushed:<br>:stuck_out_tongue_closed_eyes:</p>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> Tutorial </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> Markdown </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>Markdown基本语法（hexo均支持）</title>
      <link href="/2022/04/28/Markdown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/"/>
      <url>/2022/04/28/Markdown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="1-基本语法"><a href="#1-基本语法" class="headerlink" title="1. 基本语法"></a>1. 基本语法</h1><h2 id="1-1-标题"><a href="#1-1-标题" class="headerlink" title="1.1. 标题 - #"></a>1.1. 标题 - #</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section"># h1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">## h2</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">### h3</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">#### h4</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="1-2-段落"><a href="#1-2-段落" class="headerlink" title="1.2. 段落"></a>1.2. 段落</h2><p>Markdown划分段落非常简单，就是在段落前后保留一个空行即可</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">段落一</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">段落二</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>段落一</p><p>段落二</p><h2 id="1-3-区块引用-gt"><a href="#1-3-区块引用-gt" class="headerlink" title="1.3. 区块引用 - &gt;"></a>1.3. 区块引用 - &gt;</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; 引用段落，高亮显示</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt;                          # 空格</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; 嵌套1</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; 嵌套2</span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt;&gt; 嵌套3</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>引用段落，高亮显示</p><p>嵌套1</p><blockquote><p>嵌套2</p><blockquote><p>嵌套3</p></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote><h2 id="1-4-超链接-显示文字-超链接"><a href="#1-4-超链接-显示文字-超链接" class="headerlink" title="1.4. 超链接 - [显示文字](超链接)"></a>1.4. 超链接 - [显示文字](超链接)</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[<span class="string">超链接显示文字</span>](<span class="link">http://www.baidu.com &quot;超链接title&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><a href="http://www.baidu.com/" title="超链接title">超链接显示文字</a></p><h2 id="1-5-图片"><a href="#1-5-图片" class="headerlink" title="1.5. 图片 - ![]()"></a>1.5. 图片 - ![]()</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![<span class="string">百度logo</span>](<span class="link">https://www.baidu.com/img/bd_logo1.png?where=super</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="1-6-列表"><a href="#1-6-列表" class="headerlink" title="1.6. 列表 - +,*,-"></a>1.6. 列表 - +,*,-</h2><h3 id="1-6-1-无序列表"><a href="#1-6-1-无序列表" class="headerlink" title="1.6.1. 无序列表"></a>1.6.1. 无序列表</h3><p>不同符号最高支持到三级列表</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> 段1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">+</span> 段2</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">*</span> 段3</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">  *</span> 段3.1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">    *</span> 段3.1.1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">      *</span> 段3.1.1.1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>段1</li></ul><ul><li>段2</li></ul><ul><li>段3<ul><li>段3.1<ul><li>段3.1.1</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul><h3 id="1-6-2-有序列表"><a href="#1-6-2-有序列表" class="headerlink" title="1.6.2. 有序列表"></a>1.6.2. 有序列表</h3><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1.</span> 段1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">2.</span> 段2</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">3.</span> 段3</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">   1.</span> 段3.1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">      1.</span> 段3.1.1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li>段1</li><li>段2</li><li>段3<ol><li>段3.1<ol><li>段3.1.1</li></ol></li></ol></li></ol><h2 id="1-7-分隔线-—"><a href="#1-7-分隔线-—" class="headerlink" title="1.7. 分隔线 - ***,—"></a>1.7. 分隔线 - ***,—</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section"><span class="strong">**<span class="emphasis">*</span></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong"><span class="section">---</span></span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><hr><h2 id="1-8-字体特效"><a href="#1-8-字体特效" class="headerlink" title="1.8. 字体特效"></a>1.8. 字体特效</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">*字体1*</span>         斜体</span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">_字体1_</span>         斜体</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">**字体2**</span>       加粗</span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">__字体2__</span>       加粗</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">**<span class="emphasis">*字体3*</span>**</span>     加粗斜体</span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">__<span class="emphasis">_字体3_</span>__</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">~~字体4~~       划线</span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">`字体5`</span>         高亮</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th align="center">斜体</th><th align="center">加粗</th><th align="center">加粗斜体</th><th align="center">划线</th><th align="center">高亮</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center"><em>字体1</em></td><td align="center"><strong>字体2</strong></td><td align="center"><em><strong>字体3</strong></em></td><td align="center"><del>字体4</del></td><td align="center"><code>字体5</code></td></tr><tr><td align="center"><em>字体1</em></td><td align="center"><strong>字体2</strong></td><td align="center"><em><strong>字体3</strong></em></td><td align="center"></td><td align="center"></td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="1-9-表格"><a href="#1-9-表格" class="headerlink" title="1.9. 表格"></a>1.9. 表格</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">| 表头 | 表头 | 表头 |</span><br><span class="line">| :---- | ----: | :----: |    #分别为左对齐、右对齐、居中对齐</span><br><span class="line">| 内容 | 内容 | 内容 |</span><br><span class="line">| 内容 | 内容 | 内容 |</span><br><span class="line">| 内容 | 内容 | 内容 |</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th align="left">表头</th><th align="right">表头</th><th align="center">表头</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left">内容</td><td align="right">内容</td><td align="center">内容</td></tr><tr><td align="left">内容</td><td align="right">内容</td><td align="center">内容</td></tr><tr><td align="left">内容</td><td align="right">内容</td><td align="center">内容</td></tr></tbody></table>]]></content>
      
      
